          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p><strong>Meanwhile</strong>, add 1 tbsp <span class=\"text-danger\">(2 tbsp)</span> vegetable oil to a baking tray</p>\r\n<p><strong>Add</strong> the cayenne pepper (can't handle the heat? Go easy!), half the garlic and a generous amount of salt and pepper straight onto the baking tray</p>\r\n<p><strong>Mix</strong> the oil, garlic and spice well with a spatula or spoon</p>",
